  PROPERTIES

    CaptionML=[ENU=E.R.-2;
               ENN=E.R.-2];
    OnPreReport=BEGIN
                  IF ReturnYear = 0 THEN
                    ERROR(Text16500);

                  StartingDate := DMY2DATE(1,ReturnMonth + 1,ReturnYear);
                  IF ReturnMonth = 11 THEN
                    EndingDate := DMY2DATE(31,ReturnMonth + 1,ReturnYear)
                  ELSE
                    EndingDate := CALCDATE('-1D',DMY2DATE(1,ReturnMonth + 2,ReturnYear));

                  CompanyInformation.GET;
                END;

  }
  DATASET
  {
    { 5290;    ;DataItem;Title               ;
               DataItemTable=Table2000000026;
               DataItemTableView=SORTING(Number)
                                 WHERE(Number=CONST(1));
               OnPreDataItem=BEGIN
                               Month := ReturnMonth + 1;
                               IF STRLEN(FORMAT(Month,0)) = 1 THEN
                                 DisplayMonth := '0' + FORMAT(Month,0)
                               ELSE
                                 DisplayMonth := FORMAT(Month,0);
                             END;
                              }

    { 1500000;1;Column  ;V2__Caption         ;
               SourceExpr=V2__CaptionLbl }

    { 1500074;1;Column  ;CTSH_No_Caption     ;
               SourceExpr=CTSH_No_CaptionLbl }

    { 6787;    ;DataItem;                    ;
               DataItemTable=Table16564;
               DataItemTableView=SORTING(Excise Prod. Posting Group,Unit,BED %,AED(GSI) % / Amount,SED % / Amount,SAED % / Amount,CESS % / Amount,NCCD % / Amount,eCess % / Amount,AED (TTA) % / Amount,ADET % / Amount,ADE % / Amount,SHE Cess % / Amount)
                                 WHERE(Excise Prod. Posting Group=FILTER(<>''),
                                       Supplementary=FILTER(No));
               OnPreDataItem=BEGIN
                               SETRANGE("Posting Date",StartingDate,EndingDate);
                               IF LocationNo <> '' THEN
                                 SETRANGE("E.C.C No.",LocationNo);

                               flag := FALSE;

                               QuantityRemovedwithduty1 := 0;
                               AssessableValue1 := 0;
                               // ER2GroupFooter5Show := TRUE;
                               // ER2GroupFooter6Show := TRUE;
                             END;

               OnAfterGetRecord=BEGIN
                                  IF ECCNoItemCategory.GET("Item No.","E.C.C No.") THEN;
                                  IF ((CompanyInformation."Large Tax Payer" = TRUE) AND ("Assessable Value" = 0) AND (Type = Type::Transfer) AND
                                      (ECCNoItemCategory."Type of Item" = ECCNoItemCategory."Type of Item"::Intermediate))
                                  THEN
                                    CurrReport.SKIP;

                                  RG23APartII.RESET;
                                  CENVATAmount := 0;
                                  SEDAmount := 0;
                                  AEDAmount := 0;
                                  SAEDAmount := 0;
                                  CESSAmount := 0;
                                  eCESSAmount := 0;
                                  NCCDAmount := 0;
                                  AEDTTAAmount := 0;
                                  ADETAmount := 0;
                                  ADEAmount := 0;
                                  SHECessAmount := 0;

                                  RG23APartII.SETRANGE("Posting Date",StartingDate,EndingDate);
                                  RG23APartII.SETRANGE("Location E.C.C. No.",LocationNo);
                                  RG23APartII.SETRANGE("Excise Prod. Posting Group","Excise Prod. Posting Group");
                                  RG23APartII.SETRANGE("Type of Unit",RG23CPARTII."Type of Unit"::"100% EOU");
                                  IF RG23APartII.FINDSET THEN
                                    REPEAT
                                      CENVATAmount := RG23APartII."Total BED Amount";
                                      SEDAmount := RG23APartII."Total SED Amount";
                                      AEDAmount := RG23APartII."Total AED(GSI) Amount";
                                      AEDTTAAmount := RG23APartII."Total AED(TTA) Amount";
                                      SAEDAmount := RG23APartII."Total SAED Amount";
                                      CESSAmount := RG23APartII."Total CESS Amount";
                                      eCESSAmount := RG23APartII."Total eCess Amount";
                                      NCCDAmount := RG23APartII."Total NCCD Amount";
                                      ADETAmount := RG23APartII."Total ADET Amount";
                                      ADEAmount := RG23APartII."Total ADE Amount";
                                      SHECessAmount := RG23APartII."Total SHE Cess Amount";
                                    UNTIL RG23APartII.NEXT = 0;

                                  // initialization for group stimulation
                                  IF flag = FALSE THEN BEGIN
                                    EProdPostingGroup1 := "Excise Prod. Posting Group";
                                    Unit1 := Unit;
                                    BED1 := "BED %";
                                    AEDGSI := "AED(GSI) % / Amount";
                                    SED1 := "SED % / Amount";
                                    SAED1 := "SAED % / Amount";
                                    CESS1 := "CESS % / Amount";
                                    NCCD1 := "NCCD % / Amount";
                                    eCess1 := "eCess % / Amount";
                                    AEDTTA := "AED (TTA) % / Amount";
                                    ADET1 := "ADET % / Amount";
                                    ADE1 := "ADE % / Amount";
                                    SHE1 := "SHE Cess % / Amount";
                                  END;

                                  // Simulation of group
                                  IF (EProdPostingGroup1 <> "Excise Prod. Posting Group") OR
                                     (Unit1 <> Unit) OR
                                     (BED1 <> "BED %" ) OR
                                     (AEDGSI <> "AED(GSI) % / Amount" ) OR
                                     (SED1 <> "SED % / Amount" ) OR
                                     (SAED1 <> "SAED % / Amount" ) OR
                                     (CESS1 <> "CESS % / Amount" ) OR
                                     (NCCD1 <> "NCCD % / Amount" ) OR
                                     (eCess1 <> "eCess % / Amount" ) OR
                                     (AEDTTA <> "AED (TTA) % / Amount") OR
                                     (ADET1 <> "ADET % / Amount") OR
                                     (ADE1 <> "ADE % / Amount") OR
                                     (SHE1 <> "SHE Cess % / Amount") OR (flag = FALSE)
                                  THEN BEGIN
                                    ER2GroupFooter5Show := TRUE;
                                    ER2GroupFooter6Show := TRUE;

                                    IF flag = TRUE THEN BEGIN
                                      ER2GroupFooter5Show := (SHE1 <> "SHE Cess % / Amount");
                                      ER2GroupFooter6Show := (Unit1 <> Unit);
                                    END;
                                    flag := TRUE;
                                    // Form group header 1
                                    IF EProdPostingGroup1 <> "Excise Prod. Posting Group" THEN BEGIN
                                      InitialiseVariables;
                                      QtyCleared := 0;
                                    END;

                                    // From group header 2
                                    IF Unit1 <> Unit THEN BEGIN
                                      InitialiseVariables;
                                      IfPrinted := FALSE;
                                      QtyCleared := 0;
                                      "ERSale/Transfer".RESET;
                                      "ERSale/Transfer".SETRANGE("Posting Date",StartingDate,EndingDate);
                                      IF LocationNo <> '' THEN
                                        "ERSale/Transfer".SETRANGE("E.C.C No.",LocationNo);
                                      "ERSale/Transfer".SETRANGE("Excise Prod. Posting Group","Excise Prod. Posting Group");
                                      "ERSale/Transfer".SETRANGE(Unit,Unit);
                                      "ERSale/Transfer".SETFILTER(Type,'%1|%2',Type::Sale,Type::Transfer);
                                      IF "ERSale/Transfer".FINDFIRST THEN
                                        "Sales/TransferExist" := TRUE
                                      ELSE
                                        "Sales/TransferExist" := FALSE;
                                    END;

                                    // From group header 3
                                    "Sale/TransferEntryFound" := FALSE;

                                    QtyClearedBak := QtyCleared;

                                    // reset for next group
                                    EProdPostingGroup1 := "Excise Prod. Posting Group";
                                    Unit1 := Unit;
                                    BED1 := "BED %";
                                    AEDGSI := "AED(GSI) % / Amount";
                                    SED1 := "SED % / Amount";
                                    SAED1 := "SAED % / Amount";
                                    CESS1 := "CESS % / Amount";
                                    NCCD1 := "NCCD % / Amount";
                                    eCess1 := "eCess % / Amount";
                                    AEDTTA := "AED (TTA) % / Amount";
                                    ADET1 := "ADET % / Amount";
                                    ADE1 := "ADE % / Amount";
                                    SHE1 := "SHE Cess % / Amount";

                                    E_R__2__GroupCondition5 := FORMAT("Excise Prod. Posting Group") + FORMAT(Unit) + FORMAT("BED %");
                                    E_R__2__GroupCondition5 += FORMAT("AED(GSI) % / Amount") + FORMAT("SED % / Amount") + FORMAT("SAED % / Amount");
                                    E_R__2__GroupCondition5 += FORMAT("CESS % / Amount") + FORMAT("NCCD % / Amount") + FORMAT("eCess % / Amount");
                                    E_R__2__GroupCondition5 += FORMAT("AED (TTA) % / Amount") + FORMAT("ADET % / Amount");
                                    E_R__2__GroupCondition5 += FORMAT("ADE % / Amount") + FORMAT("SHE Cess % / Amount");

                                    // reset to calculate group totals
                                    QuantityRemovedwithduty1 := 0;
                                    AssessableValue1 := 0;
                                  END;

                                  // caculate group totals for new client
                                  QuantityRemovedwithduty1 += "Quantity Removed(with duty)";
                                  AssessableValue1 += "Assessable Value";

                                  // From body
                                  PostedStrOrderLineDetails.RESET;
                                  PostedStrOrderLineDetails.SETRANGE("Invoice No.","Order No.");
                                  PostedStrOrderLineDetails.SETRANGE("Manually Changed",TRUE);
                                  PostedStrOrderLineDetails.SETRANGE(Type,PostedStrOrderLineDetails.Type::Sale);
                                  PostedStrOrderLineDetails.SETFILTER("Document Type",'%1|%2',PostedStrOrderLineDetails."Document Type"::Invoice,
                                    PostedStrOrderLineDetails."Document Type"::Order);
                                  PostedStrOrderLineDetails.SETRANGE("Tax/Charge Code",'EXCISE');
                                  PostedStrOrderLineDetails.SETRANGE("Tax/Charge Type",PostedStrOrderLineDetails."Tax/Charge Type"::Excise);
                                  IF PostedStrOrderLineDetails.FINDFIRST THEN BEGIN
                                    CENVATAmt += "CENVAT Amount";
                                    SEDAmt += "SED Amount";
                                    AEDGSIAmt += "AED (GSI) Amount";
                                    AEDTTAAmt += "AED (TTA) Amount";
                                    SAEDAmt += "SAED Amount";
                                    CESSAmt += "CESS Amount";
                                    NCCDAmt += "NCCD Amount";
                                    ADETAmt += "ADET Amount";
                                    ADEAmt += "ADE Amount";
                                    eCESSAmt += "eCESS Amount";
                                    SHECESSAmt += "SHE Cess Amount";
                                    Amt += "Assessable Value";
                                    QtyRemWithDuty += "Quantity Removed(with duty)";
                                    QtyManufactured += "Quantity Manufactured";
                                  END;
                                  IF (Type = Type::Sale) OR (Type = Type::Transfer) THEN
                                    "Sale/TransferEntryFound" := TRUE;

                                  // Form Group footer 5 begin
                                  // ER2GroupFooter5Show := (SHE1 <> "SHE Cess % / Amount");

                                  IF "Sales/TransferExist" AND NOT "Sale/TransferEntryFound" THEN
                                    ER2GroupFooter5Show := FALSE;

                                  QtyManufactured := 0;
                                  IF (NOT IfPrinted) AND ER2GroupFooter5Show THEN BEGIN
                                    ER2OutputManf.RESET;
                                    ER2OutputManf.SETRANGE("Posting Date",StartingDate,EndingDate);
                                    IF LocationNo <> '' THEN
                                      ER2OutputManf.SETRANGE("E.C.C No.",LocationNo);
                                    ER2OutputManf.SETRANGE("Excise Prod. Posting Group","Excise Prod. Posting Group");
                                    ER2OutputManf.SETRANGE(Unit,Unit);
                                    IF ER2OutputManf.FINDSET THEN
                                      REPEAT
                                        QtyManufactured += ER2OutputManf."Quantity Manufactured";
                                        IfPrinted := TRUE;
                                      UNTIL ER2OutputManf.NEXT = 0;
                                  END;

                                  // this judgment is merged to the "SourceExpr" of control
                                  // IF  (CENVATAmt + SEDAmt + AEDGSIAmt + AEDTTAAmt + SAEDAmt + CESSAmt + NCCDAmt + ADETAmt + ADEAmt + eCESSAmt +
                                  // SHECESSAmt <> 0) THEN
                                  // ER2GroupFooter5Show := FALSE;

                                  QtyCleared := QtyClearedBak;
                                  QtyCleared += QuantityRemovedwithduty1;
                                  IF QtyCleared = 0 THEN
                                    QtyCleared += "Quantity Removed(without duty)";

                                  IF ExciseProdPostingGroup.GET("Excise Prod. Posting Group") THEN
                                    Description := COPYSTR(ExciseProdPostingGroup.Description,1,100);

                                  // group footer 5 end

                                  // For group footer 6. merged to the "SourceExpr" of control
                                  // ER2GroupFooter6Show := (Unit1 <> Unit) AND
                                  // (CENVATAmt + SEDAmt + AEDGSIAmt + AEDTTAAmt + SAEDAmt + CESSAmt + NCCDAmt + ADETAmt + ADEAmt + eCESSAmt +
                                  // SHECESSAmt <> 0);
                                END;
                                 }

    { 7724;    ;DataItem;<E.R.-2-1>          ;
               DataItemTable=Table16564;
               DataItemTableView=SORTING(Excise Prod. Posting Group,Unit)
                                 WHERE(Excise Prod. Posting Group=FILTER(<>''),
                                       Supplementary=FILTER(No));
               OnPreDataItem=BEGIN
                               SETRANGE("Posting Date",StartingDate,EndingDate);
                               IF LocationNo <> '' THEN
                                 SETRANGE("E.C.C No.",LocationNo);
                               FlagER21 := FALSE;
                             END;

               OnAfterGetRecord=BEGIN
                                  IF ECCNoItemCategory.GET("Item No.","E.C.C No.") THEN;
                                  IF NOT ((CompanyInformation."Large Tax Payer" = TRUE) AND ("Assessable Value" = 0) AND (Type = Type::Transfer) AND
                                          (ECCNoItemCategory."Type of Item" = ECCNoItemCategory."Type of Item"::Intermediate))
                                  THEN
                                    CurrReport.SKIP;

                                  IF FlagER21 = FALSE THEN BEGIN
                                    FlagER21 := TRUE;
                                    EProdPostingGroup2 := "Excise Prod. Posting Group";
                                    Unit2 := Unit;
                                  END;
                                  ER21SHOWOUTPUT := TRUE;
                                  // Simulation of group
                                  IF (EProdPostingGroup2 <> "Excise Prod. Posting Group") OR
                                     (Unit2 <> Unit)
                                  THEN BEGIN
                                    ER21SHOWOUTPUT := (Unit2 <> Unit);
                                    EProdPostingGroup2 := "Excise Prod. Posting Group";
                                    Unit2 := Unit;
                                  END;

                                  IF ExciseProdPostingGroup.GET("Excise Prod. Posting Group") THEN
                                    Description := COPYSTR(ExciseProdPostingGroup.Description,1,100);
                                END;
                                 }

    { 1672;    ;DataItem;                    ;
               DataItemTable=Table13723;
               DataItemTableView=SORTING(Posting Date)
                                 WHERE(Type of Unit=FILTER(100% EOU));
               OnPreDataItem=VAR
                               RG23APartII@1500000 : Record 13720;
                             BEGIN
                               SETRANGE("Posting Date",StartingDate,EndingDate);
                               IF LocationNo <> '' THEN
                                 SETRANGE("Location E.C.C. No.",LocationNo);
                               CENVATAmount := 0;
                               SEDAmount := 0;
                               AEDAmount := 0;
                               SAEDAmount := 0;
                               CESSAmount := 0;
                               NCCDAmount := 0;
                               AEDTTAAmount := 0;
                               ADETAmount := 0;
                               ADEAmount := 0;
                               eCESSAmount := 0;
                               SHECessAmount := 0;

                               RG23APartII.RESET;
                               RG23APartII.SETRANGE("Posting Date",StartingDate,EndingDate);
                               IF LocationNo <> '' THEN
                                 RG23APartII.SETRANGE("Location E.C.C. No.",LocationNo);
                               RG23APartII.SETRANGE("Type of Unit",RG23APartII."Type of Unit"::"100% EOU");
                               RG23APartII.SETRANGE("Excise Credit Availed as ST",FALSE);
                               IF RG23APartII.FINDSET THEN
                                 REPEAT
                                   IF RG23APartII.Type = RG23APartII.Type::Sale THEN BEGIN
                                     CENVATAmount := CENVATAmount + ABS(RG23APartII."BED Debit");
                                     // + RG23APartII."Service Tax Debit";
                                     SEDAmount := SEDAmount + ABS(RG23APartII."SED Debit");
                                     AEDAmount := AEDAmount + ABS(RG23APartII."AED(GSI) Debit");
                                     SAEDAmount := SAEDAmount + ABS(RG23APartII."SAED Debit");
                                     CESSAmount := CESSAmount + ABS(RG23APartII."CESS Debit");
                                     NCCDAmount := NCCDAmount + ABS(RG23APartII."NCCD Debit");
                                     eCESSAmount := eCESSAmount + ABS(RG23APartII."eCess Debit");
                                     // + RG23APartII."Service Tax eCess Debit");
                                     AEDTTAAmount := AEDTTAAmount + ABS(RG23APartII."AED(TTA) Debit");
                                     ADETAmount := ADETAmount + ABS(RG23APartII."ADET Debit");
                                     ADEAmount := ADEAmount + ABS(RG23APartII."ADE Debit");
                                     SHECessAmount := SHECessAmount + ABS(RG23APartII."SHE Cess Debit");
                                   END;
                                 UNTIL RG23APartII.NEXT = 0;

                               RG23CPARTII.RESET;
                               RG23CPARTII.SETRANGE("Posting Date",StartingDate,EndingDate);
                               IF LocationNo <> '' THEN
                                 RG23CPARTII.SETRANGE("Location E.C.C. No.",LocationNo);
                               RG23CPARTII.SETRANGE("Type of Unit",RG23CPARTII."Type of Unit"::"100% EOU");
                               RG23CPARTII.SETRANGE("Excise Credit Availed as ST",FALSE);
                               IF RG23CPARTII.FINDSET THEN
                                 REPEAT
                                   IF RG23CPARTII.Type = RG23CPARTII.Type::Sale THEN BEGIN
                                     CENVATAmount := CENVATAmount + ABS(RG23CPARTII."BED Debit");
                                     // + RG23CPARTII."Service Tax  Debit");
                                     SEDAmount := SEDAmount + ABS(RG23CPARTII."SED Debit");
                                     AEDAmount := AEDAmount + ABS(RG23CPARTII."AED(GSI) Debit");
                                     SAEDAmount := SAEDAmount + ABS(RG23CPARTII."SAED Debit");
                                     CESSAmount := CESSAmount + ABS(RG23CPARTII."CESS Debit");
                                     NCCDAmount := NCCDAmount + ABS(RG23CPARTII."NCCD Debit");
                                     eCESSAmount := eCESSAmount + ABS(RG23CPARTII."eCess Debit");
                                     // + RG23CPARTII."Service Tax eCess Debit");
                                     AEDTTAAmount := AEDTTAAmount + ABS(RG23CPARTII."AED(TTA) Debit");
                                     ADETAmount := ADETAmount + ABS(RG23CPARTII."ADET Debit");
                                     ADEAmount := ADEAmount + ABS(RG23CPARTII."ADE Debit");
                                     SHECessAmount := SHECessAmount + ABS(RG23CPARTII."SHE Cess Debit");
                                   END;
                                 UNTIL RG23CPARTII.NEXT = 0;
                             END;
                              }

    { 5707;    ;DataItem;                    ;
               DataItemTable=Table123;
               DataItemTableView=SORTING(Excise Prod. Posting Group,CTSH No.)
                                 WHERE(Excise Amount=FILTER(0),
                                       Type=FILTER(Item));
               OnPreDataItem=BEGIN
                               FlagPurchLine := FALSE;
                             END;

               OnAfterGetRecord=BEGIN
                                  IF PurchInvHeader.GET("Document No.") THEN
                                    IF NOT ((PurchInvHeader."Posting Date" >= StartingDate) AND
                                            (PurchInvHeader."Posting Date" <= EndingDate))
                                    THEN
                                      CurrReport.SKIP;
                                  IF Location.GET("Location Code") THEN
                                    IF Location."E.C.C. No." <> LocationNo THEN
                                      CurrReport.SKIP;

                                  IF Item.GET("No.") THEN
                                    IF Item."Excise Prod. Posting Group" = '' THEN
                                      CurrReport.SKIP;

                                  IF ("Purch. Inv. Line"."Notification Sl. No." = '') AND ("Purch. Inv. Line"."Notification No." = '') THEN
                                    CurrReport.SKIP;

                                  // Simulation of group
                                  IF FlagPurchLine = FALSE THEN BEGIN
                                    FlagPurchLine := TRUE;
                                    ExciseProdPostingGroup1 := "Excise Prod. Posting Group";
                                    SourceDocumentNo1 := "Source Document No.";
                                    UnitofMeasure1 := "Unit of Measure";
                                  END;

                                  PurchInvLineSHOWOUTPUT := TRUE;
                                  IF (ExciseProdPostingGroup1 <> "Excise Prod. Posting Group") OR
                                     (SourceDocumentNo1 <> "Source Document No.") OR
                                     (UnitofMeasure1 <> "Unit of Measure")
                                  THEN BEGIN
                                    PurchInvLineSHOWOUTPUT := (UnitofMeasure1 <> "Unit of Measure");
                                    ExciseProdPostingGroup1 := "Excise Prod. Posting Group";
                                    SourceDocumentNo1 := "Source Document No.";
                                    UnitofMeasure1 := "Unit of Measure";
                                  END;
                                END;
                                 }

               SourceExpr="Excise Prod. Posting Group" }

               SourceExpr="Source Document No." }

    { 1432;    ;DataItem;<Integer3>          ;
               DataItemTable=Table2000000026;
               DataItemTableView=SORTING(Number)
                                 WHERE(Number=CONST(1));
               OnPreDataItem=BEGIN
                               // Opening Balances - RG23CPartII
                               OpenCenvatCG := 0.0;
                               OpenAEDCG := 0.0;
                               OpenOTHCG := 0.0;
                               OpeneCESSCG := 0.0;
                               OpenSHEeCESSCG := 0.0;
                               RG23CPARTII.RESET;
                               RG23CPARTII.SETRANGE("Posting Date",0D,StartingDate - 1);
                               IF LocationNo <> '' THEN
                                 RG23CPARTII.SETRANGE("Location E.C.C. No.",LocationNo);
                               RG23CPARTII.SETRANGE("Type of Unit",RG23CPARTII."Type of Unit"::"100% EOU");
                               IF RG23CPARTII.FINDSET THEN
                                 REPEAT
                                   OpenCenvatCG :=
                                     OpenCenvatCG + RG23CPARTII."BED Credit" + RG23CPARTII."SED Credit" + RG23CPARTII."SAED Credit" +
                                     RG23CPARTII."AED(GSI) Credit" + RG23CPARTII."ADE Credit" - RG23CPARTII."BED Debit" -
                                     RG23CPARTII."SED Debit" - RG23CPARTII."SAED Debit" - RG23CPARTII."AED(GSI) Debit" - RG23CPARTII."ADE Debit" ;
                                   OpenAEDCG := OpenAEDCG + RG23CPARTII."AED(TTA) Credit" - RG23CPARTII."AED(TTA) Debit";
                                   OpenOTHCG := OpenOTHCG + RG23CPARTII."NCCD Credit" - RG23CPARTII."NCCD Debit";
                                   OpeneCESSCG := OpeneCESSCG + RG23CPARTII."eCess Credit" - RG23CPARTII."eCess Debit";
                                   OpenSHEeCESSCG := OpenSHEeCESSCG + RG23CPARTII."SHE Cess Credit" - RG23CPARTII."SHE Cess Debit";
                                   OpenADETCG := OpenADETCG + RG23CPARTII."ADET Credit" - RG23CPARTII."ADET Debit";
                                   // OpenSTCG := OpenSTCG + RG23CPARTII."Service Tax  Credit" - RG23CPARTII."Service Tax  Debit";
                                   // OpenSTeCessCG := OpenSTeCessCG + RG23CPARTII."Service Tax eCess Credit" - RG23CPARTII."Service Tax eCess Debit";
                                 UNTIL RG23CPARTII.NEXT = 0;

                               // Credit Availed - RG23CPartII
                               CrCenvatTakeCG := 0.0;
                               CrAEDTakeCG := 0.0;
                               CrOTHTakeCG := 0.0;
                               CreCESSTakeCG := 0.0;
                               CrSHEeCESSTakeCG := 0.0;
                               CrADETTakeCG := 0.0;
                               RG23CPARTII.RESET;
                               RG23CPARTII.SETRANGE("Posting Date",StartingDate,EndingDate);
                               IF LocationNo <> '' THEN
                                 RG23CPARTII.SETRANGE("Location E.C.C. No.",LocationNo);
                               RG23CPARTII.SETRANGE("Type of Unit",RG23CPARTII."Type of Unit"::"100% EOU");
                               IF RG23CPARTII.FINDSET THEN
                                 REPEAT
                                   CrCenvatTakeCG :=
                                     CrCenvatTakeCG + RG23CPARTII."BED Credit" / 2 + RG23CPARTII."SED Credit" / 2 + RG23CPARTII."SAED Credit" / 2 +
                                     RG23CPARTII."AED(GSI) Credit" / 2 + RG23CPARTII."ADE Credit" / 2;
                                   CrAEDTakeCG := CrAEDTakeCG + RG23CPARTII."AED(TTA) Credit" / 2;
                                   CrOTHTakeCG := CrOTHTakeCG + RG23CPARTII."NCCD Credit" / 2;
                                   CreCESSTakeCG := CreCESSTakeCG + RG23CPARTII."eCess Credit" / 2;
                                   CrSHEeCESSTakeCG := CrSHEeCESSTakeCG + RG23CPARTII."SHE Cess Credit" / 2;
                                   CrADETTakeCG := CrADETTakeCG + RG23CPARTII."ADET Credit" / 2;
                                   // CrSTTakeCG := CrSTTakeCG + RG23CPARTII."Service Tax  Credit" / 2;
                                   // CrSTeCessTakeCG := CrSTeCessTakeCG + RG23CPARTII."Service Tax eCess Credit" / 2;
                                   IF RG23CPARTII.Type = RG23CPARTII.Type::Purchase THEN BEGIN
                                     CrCenvatTakeCG :=
                                       CrCenvatTakeCG - RG23CPARTII."BED Debit" - RG23CPARTII."SED Debit" - RG23CPARTII."SAED Debit" -
                                       RG23CPARTII."AED(GSI) Debit" - RG23CPARTII."ADE Debit";
                                     CrAEDTakeCG := CrAEDTakeCG - RG23CPARTII."AED(TTA) Debit";
                                     CrOTHTakeCG := CrOTHTakeCG - RG23CPARTII."NCCD Debit";
                                     CreCESSTakeCG := CreCESSTakeCG - RG23CPARTII."eCess Debit";
                                     CrSHEeCESSTakeCG := CrSHEeCESSTakeCG - RG23CPARTII."SHE Cess Debit";
                                     CrADETTakeCG := CrADETTakeCG - RG23CPARTII."ADET Debit";
                                     // CrSTTakeCG := CrSTTakeCG + RG23CPARTII."Service Tax  Debit";
                                     // CrSTeCessTakeCG := CrSTeCessTakeCG + RG23CPARTII."Service Tax eCess Debit";
                                   END
                                 UNTIL RG23CPARTII.NEXT = 0;

                               // Credit Used - RG23CPartII
                               CrCenvatUsedCG := 0.0;
                               CrAEDUsedCG := 0.0;
                               CrOTHUsedCG := 0.0;
                               CreCESSUsedCG := 0.0;
                               CrSHEeCESSUsedCG := 0.0;
                               CrADETUsedCG := 0.0;
                               RG23CPARTII.RESET;
                               RG23CPARTII.SETRANGE("Posting Date",StartingDate,EndingDate);
                               RG23CPARTII.SETRANGE(Type,RG23CPARTII.Type::Sale);
                               IF LocationNo <> '' THEN
                                 RG23CPARTII.SETRANGE("Location E.C.C. No.",LocationNo);
                               RG23CPARTII.SETRANGE("Type of Unit",RG23CPARTII."Type of Unit"::"100% EOU");
                               IF RG23CPARTII.FINDSET THEN
                                 REPEAT
                                   IF NOT RG23CPARTII."Excise Credit Availed as ST" THEN BEGIN
                                     CrCenvatUsedCG :=
                                       CrCenvatUsedCG + RG23CPARTII."BED Debit" + RG23CPARTII."SED Debit" + RG23CPARTII."SAED Debit" +
                                       RG23CPARTII."ADE Debit" + RG23CPARTII."AED(GSI) Debit";
                                     CrAEDUsedCG := CrAEDUsedCG + RG23CPARTII."AED(TTA) Debit";
                                     CrOTHUsedCG := CrOTHUsedCG + RG23CPARTII."NCCD Debit";
                                     CreCESSUsedCG := CreCESSUsedCG + RG23CPARTII."eCess Debit";
                                     CrSHEeCESSUsedCG := CrSHEeCESSUsedCG + RG23CPARTII."SHE Cess Debit";
                                     CrADETUsedCG := CrADETUsedCG + RG23CPARTII."ADET Debit";
                                     // CrSTUsedCG := CrSTUsedCG + RG23CPARTII."Service Tax  Debit";
                                     // CrSTeCessUsedCG := CrSTeCessUsedCG + RG23CPARTII."Service Tax eCess Debit";
                                   END;
                                 UNTIL RG23CPARTII.NEXT = 0;

                               // Closing Balance - RG23CPartII
                               CloseCenvatCG := OpenCenvatCG + CrCenvatTakeCG - CrCenvatUsedCG;
                               CloseAEDCG := OpenAEDCG + CrAEDTakeCG - CrAEDUsedCG;
                               CloseOTHCG := OpenOTHCG + CrOTHTakeCG - CrOTHUsedCG;
                               CloseeCESSCG := OpeneCESSCG + CreCESSTakeCG - CreCESSUsedCG;
                               CloseSHEeCESSCG := OpenSHEeCESSCG + CrSHEeCESSTakeCG - CrSHEeCESSUsedCG;
                               CloseADETCG := OpenADETCG + CrADETTakeCG - CrADETUsedCG;
                               CloseSTCG := OpenSTCG + CrSTTakeCG - CrSTUsedCG;
                               CloseSTeCessCG := OpenSTeCessCG + CrSTeCessTakeCG - CrSTeCessUsedCG;

                               // Opening Balance - RG23APartII
                               OpenCenvatIN := 0.0;
                               OpenAEDIN := 0.0;
                               OpenOTHIN := 0.0;
                               OpeneCESSIN := 0.0;
                               OpenSHEeCESSIN := 0.0;
                               OpenADETIN := 0.0;
                               RG23APartII.RESET;
                               RG23APartII.SETRANGE("Posting Date",0D,StartingDate - 1);
                               IF LocationNo <> '' THEN
                                 RG23APartII.SETRANGE("Location E.C.C. No.",LocationNo);
                               RG23APartII.SETRANGE("Type of Unit",RG23APartII."Type of Unit"::"100% EOU");
                               IF RG23APartII.FINDSET THEN
                                 REPEAT
                                   OpenCenvatIN := OpenCenvatIN + RG23APartII."BED Credit" - RG23APartII."BED Debit" +
                                     RG23APartII."SED Credit" - RG23APartII."SED Debit" +
                                     RG23APartII."SAED Credit" - RG23APartII."SAED Debit" +
                                     RG23APartII."ADE Credit" - RG23APartII."ADE Debit" +
                                     RG23APartII."AED(GSI) Credit" - RG23APartII."AED(GSI) Debit";
                                   OpenAEDIN := OpenAEDIN + RG23APartII."AED(TTA) Credit" - RG23APartII."AED(TTA) Debit";
                                   OpenOTHIN := OpenOTHIN + RG23APartII."NCCD Credit" - RG23APartII."NCCD Debit";
                                   OpeneCESSIN := OpeneCESSIN + RG23APartII."eCess Credit" - RG23APartII."eCess Debit";
                                   OpenSHEeCESSIN := OpenSHEeCESSIN + RG23APartII."SHE Cess Credit" - RG23APartII."SHE Cess Debit";
                                   OpenADETIN := OpenADETIN + RG23APartII."ADET Credit" - RG23APartII."ADET Debit";
                                   // OpenSTIN := OpenSTIN + RG23APartII."Service Tax Credit" - RG23APartII."Service Tax Debit";
                                   // OpenSTeCessIN := OpenSTeCessIN + RG23APartII."Service Tax eCess Credit" - RG23APartII."Service Tax eCess Debit";
                                 UNTIL RG23APartII.NEXT = 0;

                               SerTaxEntryDetail.RESET;
                               SerTaxEntryDetail.SETRANGE("Posting Date",0D,StartingDate - 1);
                               IF LocationNo <> '' THEN
                                 SerTaxEntryDetail.SETRANGE("Location E.C.C. No.",LocationNo);
                               SerTaxEntryDetail.SETRANGE("Type of Unit",SerTaxEntryDetail."Type of Unit"::"100% EOU");
                               IF SerTaxEntryDetail.FINDSET THEN
                                 REPEAT
                                   OpenSTIN := OpenSTIN + SerTaxEntryDetail."Remaining Credit";
                                   OpenSTeCessIN := OpenSTeCessIN + SerTaxEntryDetail."Remaining Credit (eCess)";
                                   OpenSTSHEeCessIN := OpenSTSHEeCessIN + SerTaxEntryDetail."Remaining Credit (SHECess)";
                                 UNTIL (SerTaxEntryDetail.NEXT = 0);

                               RG23APartII.RESET;
                               RG23APartII.SETRANGE("Posting Date",StartingDate,EndingDate);
                               IF LocationNo <> '' THEN
                                 RG23APartII.SETRANGE("Location E.C.C. No.",LocationNo);
                               RG23APartII.SETRANGE("Type of Unit",RG23APartII."Type of Unit"::"100% EOU");
                               RG23APartII.SETRANGE("Excise Credit Availed as ST",TRUE);
                               IF RG23APartII.FINDSET THEN
                                 REPEAT
                                   CrSTTakeIN :=
                                     CrSTTakeIN + RG23APartII."BED Debit" + RG23APartII."AED(GSI) Debit" + RG23APartII."SED Debit" + RG23APartII."SAED Debit" +
                                     RG23APartII."NCCD Debit" + RG23APartII."ADET Debit" + RG23APartII."AED(TTA) Debit" + RG23APartII."ADE Debit" +
                                     RG23APartII."ADC VAT Debit";
                                   CrSTeCessTakeIN := CrSTeCessTakeIN + RG23APartII."eCess Debit";
                                   CrSTSHEeCessTakeIN := CrSTSHEeCessTakeIN + RG23APartII."eCess Debit";
                                 UNTIL (RG23APartII.NEXT = 0);

                               RG23CPARTII.RESET;
                               RG23CPARTII.SETRANGE("Posting Date",StartingDate,EndingDate);
                               RG23CPARTII.SETRANGE("Excise Credit Availed as ST",TRUE);
                               IF LocationNo <> '' THEN
                                 RG23CPARTII.SETRANGE("Location E.C.C. No.",LocationNo);
                               RG23CPARTII.SETRANGE("Type of Unit",RG23CPARTII."Type of Unit"::"100% EOU");
                               IF RG23CPARTII.FINDSET THEN
                                 REPEAT
                                   CrSTTakeCG :=
                                     CrSTTakeCG + RG23CPARTII."BED Debit" + RG23CPARTII."AED(GSI) Debit" + RG23CPARTII."SAED Debit" + RG23CPARTII."CESS Debit" +
                                     RG23CPARTII."NCCD Debit" + RG23CPARTII."SED Debit" + RG23CPARTII."ADET Debit" + RG23CPARTII."AED(TTA) Debit" +
                                     RG23CPARTII."ADE Debit" + RG23CPARTII."ADC VAT Debit";
                                   CrSTeCessTakeCG := CrSTeCessTakeCG + RG23CPARTII."eCess Debit" ;
                                   CrSTeCessTakeCG := CrSTSHEeCessTakeCG + RG23CPARTII."SHE Cess Debit";
                                 UNTIL (RG23CPARTII.NEXT = 0);

                               {ServiceTaxDetail.RESET;
                               ServiceTaxDetail.SETRANGE("Posting Date",StartingDate,EndingDate);
                               IF LocationNo <> '' THEN
                                 ServiceTaxDetail.SETRANGE("Location E.C.C. No.",LocationNo);
                               ServiceTaxDetail.SETRANGE(Type,RG23APartII.Type::Sale);
                               ServiceTaxDetail.SETRANGE("Type of Unit",ServiceTaxDetail."Type of Unit"::"100% EOU");
                               IF ServiceTaxDetail.FINDSET THEN
                                 REPEAT
                                   CrSTUtilisedServices := CrSTUtilisedServices + ServiceTaxDetail."Service Tax Amount";
                                   CrSTeCessUtilisedServices := CrSTeCessUtilisedServices + ServiceTaxDetail."Service Tax eCess Amount" ;
                                 UNTIL (ServiceTaxDetail.NEXT = 0);   }

                               ServiceTaxDetail.RESET;
                               ServiceTaxDetail.SETRANGE("Posting Date",StartingDate,EndingDate);
                               IF LocationNo <> '' THEN
                                 ServiceTaxDetail.SETRANGE("Location E.C.C. No.",LocationNo);
                               ServiceTaxDetail.SETRANGE(Type,RG23APartII.Type::Purchase);
                               ServiceTaxDetail.SETRANGE("Type of Unit",ServiceTaxDetail."Type of Unit"::"100% EOU");
                               IF ServiceTaxDetail.FINDSET THEN
                                 REPEAT
                                   CrServiceTaxIPServices := CrServiceTaxIPServices + ServiceTaxDetail."Service Tax Amount";
                                   CreCessServiceTaxIPServices := CreCessServiceTaxIPServices + ServiceTaxDetail."Service Tax eCess Amount";
                                   CrSHEeCessServiceTaxIPServices := CrSHEeCessServiceTaxIPServices + ServiceTaxDetail."Service Tax SHE Cess Amount";
                                 UNTIL (ServiceTaxDetail.NEXT = 0);

                               STasExciseUtilised.RESET;
                               STasExciseUtilised.SETRANGE("Posting Date",StartingDate,EndingDate);
                               IF LocationNo <> '' THEN
                                 STasExciseUtilised.SETRANGE("Location E.C. C. No.",LocationNo);
                               STasExciseUtilised.SETRANGE("Type of Unit",STasExciseUtilised."Type of Unit"::"100% EOU");
                               IF STasExciseUtilised.FINDSET THEN
                                 REPEAT
                                   CrSTUtilised := CrSTUtilised + STasExciseUtilised."ST as Excise Utilisation";
                                   CrSTeCessUtlised := CrSTeCessUtlised + STasExciseUtilised."ST eCess as Excise Utilisation";
                                   CrSTSHEeCessUtlised := CrSTSHEeCessUtlised + STasExciseUtilised."ST SHECess Excise Utilisation";
                                 UNTIL (STasExciseUtilised.NEXT = 0);

                               STPaymentECCNo.RESET;
                               STPaymentECCNo.SETRANGE("Posting Date",StartingDate,EndingDate);
                               IF LocationNo <> '' THEN
                                 STPaymentECCNo.SETRANGE("Location E.C.C. No.",LocationNo);
                               STPaymentECCNo.SETRANGE("Type of Unit",STPaymentECCNo."Type of Unit"::"100% EOU");
                               IF STPaymentECCNo.FINDSET THEN
                                 REPEAT
                                   CrSTUtilisedServices := CrSTUtilisedServices + STPaymentECCNo."Credit availed";
                                   CrSTeCessUtilisedServices := CrSTeCessUtilisedServices + STPaymentECCNo."Credit availed (eCess)";
                                   CrSTSHEeCessUtilisedServices := CrSTSHEeCessUtilisedServices + STPaymentECCNo."Credit availed (SHECess)";
                                 UNTIL (STPaymentECCNo.NEXT = 0);

                               RG23APartII.RESET;
                               RG23APartII.SETRANGE("Posting Date",StartingDate,EndingDate);
                               IF LocationNo <> '' THEN
                                 RG23APartII.SETRANGE("Location E.C.C. No.",LocationNo);
                               RG23APartII.SETRANGE(Type,RG23APartII.Type::Sale);
                               RG23APartII.SETRANGE("Type of Unit",RG23APartII."Type of Unit"::"100% EOU");
                               RG23APartII.SETRANGE("Excise Credit Availed as ST",TRUE);
                               IF RG23APartII.FINDSET THEN
                                 REPEAT
                                   CrCenvatUtilisedServices :=
                                     CrCenvatUtilisedServices + RG23APartII."BED Debit" + RG23APartII."SED Debit" +
                                     RG23APartII."SAED Debit" + RG23APartII."AED(GSI) Debit" + RG23APartII."ADET Debit";
                                   CrAEDTTAUtilisedServices := CrAEDTTAUtilisedServices + RG23APartII."AED(TTA) Debit";
                                   CrOTHUtilisedServices := CrOTHUtilisedServices + RG23APartII."NCCD Debit";
                                   CreCessUtilisedServices := CreCessUtilisedServices + RG23APartII."eCess Debit";
                                   CrSHEeCessUtilisedServices := CrSHEeCessUtilisedServices + RG23APartII."SHE Cess Debit";
                                   // CrADEUtilisedServices := CrADEUtlisedServices + RG23APartII."ADE Debit";
                                   // CrADCUtilisedServices := CrADCUtilisedServices+ RG23APartII."ADC VAT Debit";
                                 UNTIL RG23APartII.NEXT = 0;

                               RG23CPARTII.SETRANGE("Posting Date",StartingDate,EndingDate);
                               IF LocationNo <> '' THEN
                                 RG23CPARTII.SETRANGE("Location E.C.C. No.",LocationNo);
                               RG23CPARTII.SETRANGE(Type,RG23APartII.Type::Sale);
                               RG23CPARTII.SETRANGE("Type of Unit",RG23CPARTII."Type of Unit"::"100% EOU");
                               RG23CPARTII.SETRANGE("Excise Credit Availed as ST",TRUE);
                               IF RG23CPARTII.FINDSET THEN
                                 REPEAT
                                   CrCenvatUtilisedServices :=
                                     CrCenvatUtilisedServices + RG23CPARTII."BED Debit" + RG23CPARTII."SED Debit" +
                                     RG23CPARTII."SAED Debit" + RG23CPARTII."AED(GSI) Debit" + RG23CPARTII."ADET Debit";
                                   CrAEDTTAUtilisedServices := CrAEDTTAUtilisedServices + RG23CPARTII."AED(TTA) Debit";
                                   CrOTHUtilisedServices := CrOTHUtilisedServices + RG23CPARTII."NCCD Debit";
                                   CreCessUtilisedServices := CreCessUtilisedServices + RG23CPARTII."eCess Debit";
                                   CrSHEeCessUtilisedServices := CrSHEeCessUtilisedServices + RG23CPARTII."SHE Cess Debit";
                                   // CrADEUtlisedServices := CrADEUtlisedServices + RG23CPARTII."ADE Debit";
                                   // CrADCUtilisedServices := CrADCUtilisedServices+ RG23CPARTII."ADC VAT Debit";
                                 UNTIL RG23APartII.NEXT = 0;

                               // Credit Availed - RG23APartII
                               CrCenvatTakeIN := 0;
                               CrAEDTakeIN := 0;
                               CrOTHTakeIN := 0;
                               CreCESSTakeIN := 0;
                               CrSHEeCESSTakeIN := 0;
                               CrADETTakeIN := 0;
                               RG23APartII.RESET;
                               RG23APartII.SETRANGE("Posting Date",StartingDate,EndingDate);
                               IF LocationNo <> '' THEN
                                 RG23APartII.SETRANGE("Location E.C.C. No.",LocationNo);
                               RG23APartII.SETRANGE("Type of Unit",RG23APartII."Type of Unit"::"100% EOU");
                               IF RG23APartII.FINDSET THEN
                                 REPEAT
                                   CrCenvatTakeIN :=
                                     CrCenvatTakeIN + RG23APartII."BED Credit" + RG23APartII."SED Credit" +
                                     RG23APartII."SAED Credit" + RG23APartII."ADE Credit" + RG23APartII."AED(GSI) Credit";
                                   CrAEDTakeIN := CrAEDTakeIN + RG23APartII."AED(TTA) Credit";
                                   CrOTHTakeIN := CrOTHTakeIN + RG23APartII."NCCD Credit";
                                   CreCESSTakeIN := CreCESSTakeIN + RG23APartII."eCess Credit";
                                   CrSHEeCESSTakeIN := CrSHEeCESSTakeIN + RG23APartII."SHE Cess Credit";
                                   CrADETTakeIN := CrADETTakeIN + RG23APartII."ADET Credit";
                                   // CrSTTakeIN := CrSTTakeIN + RG23APartII."Service Tax Credit";
                                   // CrSTeCessTakeIN := CrSTeCessTakeIN + RG23APartII."Service Tax eCess Credit";
                                   IF RG23APartII.Type = RG23APartII.Type::Purchase THEN BEGIN
                                     CrCenvatTakeIN :=
                                       CrCenvatTakeIN - RG23APartII."BED Debit" - RG23APartII."SED Debit" - RG23APartII."SAED Debit" -
                                       RG23APartII."ADE Debit" - RG23APartII."AED(GSI) Debit";
                                     CrAEDTakeIN := CrAEDTakeIN - RG23APartII."AED(TTA) Debit";
                                     CrOTHTakeIN := CrOTHTakeIN - RG23APartII."NCCD Debit";
                                     CreCESSTakeIN := CreCESSTakeIN - RG23APartII."eCess Debit";
                                     CrSHEeCESSTakeIN := CrSHEeCESSTakeIN - RG23APartII."SHE Cess Debit";
                                     CrADETTakeIN := CrADETTakeIN - RG23APartII."ADET Debit";
                                     // CrSTTakeIN := CrSTTakeIN + RG23APartII."Service Tax Debit";
                                     // CrSTeCessTakeIN := CrSTeCessTakeIN + RG23APartII."Service Tax eCess Debit";
                                   END
                                 UNTIL RG23APartII.NEXT = 0;

                               // Credit Used - RG23APartII
                               CrCenvatUsedIN := 0;
                               CrAEDUsedIN := 0;
                               CrOTHUsedIN := 0;
                               CreCESSUsedIN := 0;
                               CrSHEeCESSUsedIN := 0;
                               CrADETUsedIN := 0;
                               RG23APartII.RESET;
                               RG23APartII.SETRANGE("Posting Date",StartingDate,EndingDate);
                               IF LocationNo <> '' THEN
                                 RG23APartII.SETRANGE("Location E.C.C. No.",LocationNo);
                               RG23APartII.SETRANGE("Type of Unit",RG23APartII."Type of Unit"::"100% EOU");
                               RG23APartII.SETRANGE(Type,RG23APartII.Type::Sale);
                               IF RG23APartII.FINDSET THEN
                                 REPEAT
                                   IF NOT RG23APartII."Excise Credit Availed as ST" THEN BEGIN
                                     CrCenvatUsedIN :=
                                       CrCenvatUsedIN + RG23APartII."BED Debit" + RG23APartII."SED Debit" +
                                       RG23APartII."SAED Debit" + RG23APartII."AED(GSI) Debit" + RG23APartII."ADE Debit";
                                     CrAEDUsedIN := CrAEDUsedIN + RG23APartII."AED(TTA) Debit";
                                     CrOTHUsedIN := CrOTHUsedIN + RG23APartII."NCCD Debit";
                                     CreCESSUsedIN := CreCESSUsedIN + RG23APartII."eCess Debit";
                                     CrSHEeCESSUsedIN := CrSHEeCESSUsedIN + RG23APartII."SHE Cess Debit";
                                     CrADETUsedIN := CrADETUsedIN + RG23APartII."ADET Debit";
                                     // CrSTUsedIN := CrSTUsedIN + RG23APartII."Service Tax Debit";
                                     // CrSTeCessUsedIN := CrSTeCessUsedIN + RG23APartII."Service Tax eCess Debit";
                                   END;
                                 UNTIL RG23APartII.NEXT = 0;

                               // Closing Balance - RG23APartII
                               CloseCenvatIN := OpenCenvatIN + CrCenvatTakeIN - CrCenvatUsedIN;
                               CloseAEDIN := OpenAEDIN + CrAEDTakeIN - CrAEDUsedIN;
                               CloseOTHIN := OpenOTHIN + CrOTHTakeIN - CrOTHUsedIN;
                               CloseeCESSIN := CloseeCESSIN + CreCESSTakeIN - CreCESSUsedIN;
                               CloseSHEeCESSIN := CloseSHEeCESSIN + CrSHEeCESSTakeIN - CrSHEeCESSUsedIN;
                               CloseADETIN := CloseADETIN + CrADETTakeIN - CrADETUsedIN;
                               CloseSTIN := CloseSTIN + CrSTTakeIN - CrSTUsedIN;
                               CloseSTeCessIN := CloseSTeCessIN + CrSTeCessTakeIN - CrSTeCessUsedIN;

                               // Update PLA amount
                               PLARec.RESET;
                               PLAAmount := 0;
                               PLARec.SETRANGE("Posting Date",StartingDate,EndingDate);
                               IF LocationNo <> '' THEN
                                 PLARec.SETRANGE("Location E.C.C. No.",LocationNo);
                               PLARec.SETRANGE("Type of Unit",PLARec."Type of Unit"::"100% EOU");
                               IF PLARec.FINDSET THEN
                                 REPEAT
                                   PLAAmount :=
                                     PLAAmount + PLARec."BED Credit" + PLARec."AED(GSI) Credit" + PLARec."SED Credit" +
                                     PLARec."SAED Credit" + PLARec."CESS Credit" + PLARec."NCCD Credit" +
                                     PLARec."eCess Credit" + PLARec."Excise Charges Credit" + PLARec."ADE Credit" + PLARec."ADET Credit" +
                                     PLARec."AED(TTA) Credit" + PLARec."SHE Cess Credit";
                                 UNTIL PLARec.NEXT = 0;

                               // Update Invoice Numbers
                               ExciseEntry.SETRANGE("Posting Date",StartingDate,EndingDate);
                               ExciseEntry.SETRANGE("Document Type",ExciseEntry."Document Type"::Invoice);
                               ExciseEntry.SETRANGE("E.C.C. No.",LocationNo);
                               ExciseEntry.SETRANGE(Type,ExciseEntry.Type::Sale);
                               IF ExciseEntry.FINDFIRST THEN
                                 SlNo1 := ExciseEntry."Document No.";
                               IF ExciseEntry.FINDLAST THEN
                                 SlNo2 := ExciseEntry."Document No.";
                             END;
                              }

    { 1500050;1;Column  ;OpenCenvatIN___OpenCenvatCG;
               SourceExpr=OpenCenvatIN + OpenCenvatCG }

               SourceExpr=OpenCenvatIN + OpenCenvatCG + CrCenvatTakeIN + CrCenvatTakeCG - CrCenvatUsedIN - CrCenvatUsedCG - CrCenvatUtilisedServices }

    { 1500164;1;Column  ;OpenAEDIN___OpenAEDCG___CrAEDTakeIN___CrAEDTakeCG;
               SourceExpr=OpenAEDIN + OpenAEDCG + CrAEDTakeIN + CrAEDTakeCG }

    { 1500165;1;Column  ;OpenOTHIN___OpenOTHCG___CrOTHTakeIN___CrOTHTakeCG;
               SourceExpr=OpenOTHIN + OpenOTHCG + CrOTHTakeIN + CrOTHTakeCG }

    { 1500220;1;Column  ;OpeneCESSIN___OpeneCESSCG;
               SourceExpr=OpeneCESSIN + OpeneCESSCG }

    { 1500224;1;Column  ;CreCESSTakeIN       ;
               SourceExpr=CreCESSTakeIN }

    { 1500226;1;Column  ;CreCESSTakeCG       ;
               SourceExpr=CreCESSTakeCG }

    { 1500228;1;Column  ;OpeneCESSIN___OpeneCESSCG___CreCESSTakeIN___CreCESSTakeCG;
               SourceExpr=OpeneCESSIN + OpeneCESSCG + CreCESSTakeIN + CreCESSTakeCG }

    { 1500231;1;Column  ;OpeneCESSIN___OpeneCESSCG___CreCESSTakeIN___CreCESSTakeCG___CreCESSUsedIN_____CreCESSUsedCG___CreCessUtilisedServices;
               SourceExpr=OpeneCESSIN + OpeneCESSCG + CreCESSTakeIN + CreCESSTakeCG - CreCESSUsedIN - CreCESSUsedCG - CreCessUtilisedServices }

    { 1500307;1;Column  ;CrCenvatUsedIN___CrCenvatUsedCG___CrCenvatUtilisedRAS;
               SourceExpr=CrCenvatUsedIN + CrCenvatUsedCG - CrCenvatUtilisedRAS }

    { 1500311;1;Column  ;CrOTHUsedIN___CrOTHUsedCG___CrNCCDUtilisedRAS;
               SourceExpr=CrOTHUsedIN + CrOTHUsedCG - CrNCCDUtilisedRAS }

    { 1500313;1;Column  ;CreCESSUsedIN___CreCESSUsedCG___CreCessUtilisedRAS;
               SourceExpr=CreCESSUsedIN + CreCESSUsedCG - CreCessUtilisedRAS }

    { 1500325;1;Column  ;CrADETTakeIN        ;
               SourceExpr=CrADETTakeIN }

    { 1500326;1;Column  ;CrADETTakeCG        ;
               SourceExpr=CrADETTakeCG }

    { 1500327;1;Column  ;OpenADETIN___OpenADETCG___CrADETTakeIN___CrADETTakeCG;
               SourceExpr=OpenADETIN + OpenADETCG + CrADETTakeIN + CrADETTakeCG }

    { 1500334;1;Column  ;CrADETUsedIN___CrADETUsedCG___CrADETUtilisedRAS;
               SourceExpr=CrADETUsedIN + CrADETUsedCG - CrADETUtilisedRAS }

    { 1500338;1;Column  ;OpenADETIN___OpenADETCG___CrADETTakeIN___CrADETTakeCG___CrADETUsedIN___CrADETUsedCG;
               SourceExpr=OpenADETIN + OpenADETCG + CrADETTakeIN + CrADETTakeCG - CrADETUsedIN - CrADETUsedCG }

    { 1500351;1;Column  ;CrSTUtilised        ;
               SourceExpr=CrSTUtilised }

    { 1500355;1;Column  ;OpenSTIN___OpenSTCG___CrSTTakeIN___CrSTTakeCG___CrServiceTaxIPServices___CrSTUtilised___CrSTUtilisedServices;
               SourceExpr=OpenSTIN + OpenSTCG + CrSTTakeIN + CrSTTakeCG + CrServiceTaxIPServices - CrSTUtilised - CrSTUtilisedServices }

    { 1500363;1;Column  ;CrSTeCessTakeCG     ;
               SourceExpr=CrSTeCessTakeCG }

    { 1500366;1;Column  ;OpenSTeCessIN___OpenSTeCessCG___CrSTeCessTakeIN___CrSTeCessTakeCG___CreCessServiceTaxIPServices_;
               SourceExpr=[OpenSTeCessIN + OpenSTeCessCG + CrSTeCessTakeIN + CrSTeCessTakeCG + CreCessServiceTaxIPServices ] }

    { 1500368;1;Column  ;CrSTeCessUtlised    ;
               SourceExpr=CrSTeCessUtlised }

    { 1500372;1;Column  ;OpenSTeCessIN___OpenSTeCessCG___CrSTeCessTakeIN___CrSTeCessTakeCG___CreCessServiceTaxIPServices___CrSTeCessUtlised___CrSTeCessUtilisedServices;
               SourceExpr=OpenSTeCessIN + OpenSTeCessCG + CrSTeCessTakeIN + CrSTeCessTakeCG + CreCessServiceTaxIPServices - CrSTeCessUtlised - CrSTeCessUtilisedServices }

    { 1500324;1;Column  ;OpenADETIN___OpenADETCG;
               SourceExpr=OpenADETIN + OpenADETCG }

    { 1500344;1;Column  ;OpenSTIN___OpenSTCG ;
               SourceExpr=OpenSTIN + OpenSTCG }

    { 1500361;1;Column  ;OpenSTeCessIN___OpenSTeCessCG;
               SourceExpr=OpenSTeCessIN + OpenSTeCessCG }

    { 1500349;1;Column  ;OpenSTIN___OpenSTCG___CrSTTakeIN___CrSTTakeCG___CrServiceTaxIPServices;
               SourceExpr=OpenSTIN + OpenSTCG + CrSTTakeIN + CrSTTakeCG + CrServiceTaxIPServices }

    { 1500310;1;Column  ;CrAEDUsedIN___CrAEDUsedCG___CrAEDTTAUtilisedRAS;
               SourceExpr=CrAEDUsedIN + CrAEDUsedCG - CrAEDTTAUtilisedRAS }

    { 1500346;1;Column  ;CrSTTakeCG          ;
               SourceExpr=CrSTTakeCG }

    { 1500330;1;Column  ;CrSTTakeIN          ;
               SourceExpr=CrSTTakeIN }

    { 1500331;1;Column  ;CrSTeCessTakeIN     ;
               SourceExpr=CrSTeCessTakeIN }

    { 1500345;1;Column  ;CrServiceTaxIPServices;
               SourceExpr=CrServiceTaxIPServices }

    { 1500353;1;Column  ;CreCessServiceTaxIPServices;
               SourceExpr=CreCessServiceTaxIPServices }

    { 1500357;1;Column  ;CrSTUtilisedServices;
               SourceExpr=CrSTUtilisedServices }

    { 1500362;1;Column  ;CrSTeCessUtilisedServices;
               SourceExpr=CrSTeCessUtilisedServices }

    { 1500473;1;Column  ;CrCenvatUtilisedRAS ;
               SourceExpr=CrCenvatUtilisedRAS }

    { 1500479;1;Column  ;CrAEDTTAUtilisedRAS ;
               SourceExpr=CrAEDTTAUtilisedRAS }

    { 1500480;1;Column  ;CrNCCDUtilisedRAS   ;
               SourceExpr=CrNCCDUtilisedRAS }

    { 1500497;1;Column  ;CrADETUtilisedRAS   ;
               SourceExpr=CrADETUtilisedRAS }

    { 1500498;1;Column  ;CreCessUtilisedRAS  ;
               SourceExpr=CreCessUtilisedRAS }

    { 9072;1   ;DataItem;                    ;
               DataItemTable=Table16567;
               DataItemTableView=SORTING(Challan No.,Challan Date,Document No.)
                                 WHERE(Entry Type=FILTER(Application));
               OnPreDataItem=BEGIN
                               IF "<Integer4>".Number = 1 THEN
                                 SETFILTER("Arrears of Duty under Rule 8",'<>%1',0);
                               IF "<Integer4>".Number = 2 THEN
                                 SETFILTER("Interest Payment under Rule 8",'<>%1',0);
                               IF "<Integer4>".Number = 3 THEN
                                 SETFILTER("Misc. payments",'<>%1',0);
                               FlagDetailedPLAEntry := FALSE;
                             END;

               OnAfterGetRecord=BEGIN
                                  PLAEntry3.GET("PLA Entry No.");
                                  IF (PLAEntry3."Posting Date" < StartingDate) OR (PLAEntry3."Posting Date" > EndingDate) OR
                                     (PLAEntry3."Type of Unit" <> PLAEntry3."Type of Unit"::"100% EOU") OR
                                     ((LocationNo <> '') AND (PLAEntry3."Location E.C.C. No." <> LocationNo))
                                  THEN
                                    CurrReport.SKIP;

                                  ChangeCounter := ChangeCounter + 1;

                                  // Simulation of group
                                  IF FlagDetailedPLAEntry = FALSE THEN BEGIN
                                    FlagDetailedPLAEntry := TRUE;
                                    ChallanNo1 := "Challan No.";
                                    ChallanDate1 := "Challan Date";
                                  END;
                                  DetailedPLAEntrySHOWOUTPUT := TRUE;
                                  IF (ChallanNo1 <> "Challan No.") OR
                                     (ChallanDate1 <> "Challan Date")
                                  THEN BEGIN
                                    DetailedPLAEntrySHOWOUTPUT := (ChallanDate1 <> "Challan Date");
                                    ChallanNo1 := "Challan No.";
                                    ChallanDate1 := "Challan Date";
                                  END;
                                  IF DetailedPLAEntrySHOWOUTPUT THEN BEGIN
                                    IF  "<Integer4>".Number = 1 THEN BEGIN
                                      TextTobePrinted := 'Arrears of Duty';
                                      PLAPaymentAmt := "Arrears of Duty under Rule 8";
                                    END;
                                    IF  "<Integer4>".Number = 2 THEN BEGIN
                                      TextTobePrinted := 'Interest';
                                      PLAPaymentAmt := "Interest Payment under Rule 8";
                                    END;
                                    IF  "<Integer4>".Number = 3 THEN BEGIN
                                      TextTobePrinted := 'Misc. payments';
                                      PLAPaymentAmt := "Misc. payments";
                                    END;

                                    IF (ChangeCounter > 0) AND (NOT AmountPrinted) THEN
                                      AmountPrinted := TRUE;
                                  END;
                                END;
                                 }

    { 1500432;2;Column  ;TextTobePrinted     ;
               SourceExpr=TextTobePrinted }

    { 1500434;2;Column  ;PLAPaymentAmt       ;
               SourceExpr=PLAPaymentAmt }

    { 1500435;2;Column  ;Detailed_PLA_Entry__Challan_No__;

  <Code>Public Function BlankZero(ByVal Value As Decimal)
    if Value = 0 then
        Return ""
    end if
    Return Value
End Function

Public Function BlankPos(ByVal Value As Decimal)
    if Value &gt; 0 then
        Return ""
    end if
    Return Value
End Function

Public Function BlankZeroAndPos(ByVal Value As Decimal)
    if Value &gt;= 0 then
        Return ""
    end if
    Return Value
End Function

Public Function BlankNeg(ByVal Value As Decimal)
    if Value &lt; 0 then
        Return ""
    end if
    Return Value
End Function

Public Function BlankNegAndZero(ByVal Value As Decimal)
    if Value &lt;= 0 then
        Return ""
    end if
    Return Value
End Function
